filtered_inv_mean_freqs = read.csv('./inversion_tpt_frequencies.csv')
In [4]:
filtered_inv_mean_freqs  = filtered_inv_mean_freqs %>% rowwise() %>% mutate(phase = if_else(phase == 'expansion', 'Expansion', 'Truncation'))

filtered_inv_mean_freqs_transformed <- filtered_inv_mean_freqs %>% mutate(tpt = if_else(phase=='Truncation',5*as.numeric(tpt) / 21 + 4,as.numeric(tpt)))

In [92]:
for (inv in as.character(unique(filtered_inv_mean_freqs_transformed$inversion))){
    p = ggplot(filtered_inv_mean_freqs_transformed %>% filter(inversion == inv), aes(x=tpt,y=frequency_mean, group=phase, color=phase)) + 
      theme_bw() +
      geom_line(size = 1.5) +
      geom_point(size = 5) +
      geom_errorbar(aes(ymin=frequency_mean-frequency_se, ymax=frequency_mean+frequency_se),size = 1.5, width=.6, position=position_dodge(0.05)) +
      ggtitle(paste0(inv)) +
      ylab("") +
      scale_x_continuous(name = "Expansion Generations", breaks=c(0,1,2,3,4,6,8,9),
                     sec.axis = sec_axis(~ (.-4)*21/5, name = "Truncation Hours", breaks=c(0,6,9,12,15,19,21))) +
      guides(color=guide_legend(title="Phase")) +
      coord_cartesian(ylim=c(0.01,0.13)) +
      scale_y_continuous(breaks=c(0.01,0.03,0.05,0.07,0.09,0.11,0.13)) +
      theme(
        legend.position = "right",  # Legend position
        axis.title.x = element_text(vjust = -1),  # Move primary x-axis title
        axis.title.x.top = element_text(vjust = 0.5),  # Position for the secondary x-axis title
        axis.text.x.top = element_blank(),  # Remove top x-axis tick labels
        axis.text.x = element_text(margin = margin(t = 10)),  # Keep bottom x-axis tick labels
        axis.ticks.x.top = element_line(),  # Keep top x-axis tick marks
      legend.title=element_blank()) +
      theme(text = element_text(size = 40)) +
      scale_color_manual(values=c("purple", "orange"))
    print(p)
    ggsave(paste0(inv, '.ExpansionTruncationDynamics.pdf'),p, height = 10, width = 12)    

}

p = ggplot(filtered_inv_mean_freqs_transformed %>% filter(inversion == 'In2Lt'), aes(x=tpt,y=frequency_mean, group=phase, color=phase)) + 
  theme_bw() +
  geom_line() +
  geom_point() +
  geom_errorbar(aes(ymin=frequency_mean-frequency_se, ymax=frequency_mean+frequency_se), width=0.2, position=position_dodge(0.05)) +
  ggtitle("In3RP") +
  ylab("") +
  scale_x_continuous(name = "Expansion Generations", breaks=c(0,1,2,3,4,6,8,9),
                     sec.axis = sec_axis(~ (.-4)*21/5, name = "Truncation Hours", breaks=c(0,6,9,12,15,19,21))) +
  guides(color=guide_legend(title="Phase")) +
  coord_cartesian(ylim=c(0.01,0.13)) +
  scale_y_continuous(breaks=c(0.01,0.03,0.05,0.07,0.09,0.11,0.13)) +
  theme(
    legend.position = "right",  # Legend position
    axis.title.x = element_text(vjust = -.01),  # Move primary x-axis title
    axis.title.x.top = element_text(vjust = 0.5),  # Position for the secondary x-axis title
    axis.text.x.top = element_text(angle = 90, vjust = 0.5, hjust = 0),  # Rotate top x-axis labels 90 degrees
    axis.text.x = element_text(margin = margin(t = 10))  # Keep bottom x-axis labels
  ) +
  theme(text = element_text(size = 40)) +
  scale_color_manual(values=c("purple", "orange"))

ggsave(paste0('TestInv.ExpansionTruncationDynamics.pdf'),p, height = 10, width = 12)
